{"tid":2152274,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國傳考慮禁止TikTok上架、發布廣告 接受下載條款亦違法","createTime":"2020-08-12T01:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T02:06:00.000Z","uid":39464,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"62c0105572dbe10d088bacfd5a2eaaf2df3f3dc0","tid":2152274,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T01:42:19.000Z","msg":"路透引述白宮文件指，美國對TikTok的行政命令，可能會阻止美國應用商店上架TikTok，並且使到TikTok發布廣告、下載時接受Tiktok的服務條款亦屬違法行為。上周公布的行政命令指，如45日後未能出售TikTok，將禁止與TikTok進行交易。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1597193733473&amp;issue=20200812\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1597193733473%26issue%3D20200812&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf2ipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=3d72bd0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1597193733473&amp;issue=20200812</a>"},{"pid":"76caca7a75750c63dcd9952d276892d20525ee12","tid":2152274,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:06:00.000Z","msg":"美國公司喺入面落廣告都犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}